replies.body:
I would like to point out that if you're going to play with this team in the tournament, you're obviously getting dqed. Like no offense to Saikron or whatever his name is, but that's actually the most obvious shit I've ever seen in my entire life at 1:13+, it's like he's not even trying to hide it. He's always on the hitbox, no matter what, and as soon as the cursor starts to go outside the hitbox, it drags back just in time. It looks exactly like the client that ambi said "where's the megalink" or some shit like that.
If you really plan on playing this tournament, atleast have a legit team, and not a team that people can laugh at.
